rComments: He is by far my favorite teacher here. Only two exams, yet count a lot for your grade. They are all essay questions. I personally had to study a lot the day before exams to do as well as I did, but if you are looking for a class of interest and not an easy A dont take this class. It truly is interesting material which you can apply to actual life.
Don't be intimidated!  At first his accent, pace, and the content of the class may seem difficult, but the exams are graded easy.
